<font color="#FF0000">HOW TO FIND YOUR BUDDIES</font><br>
<tt>Sun Jun 22 12:23:01 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
To all my brothers and sisters Viet-Nam Veterans I would <br>
like to provide you with a web-site that enables you to find<br>
some of your old buddies. I found some of my old friends<br>
that I had served in Viet-Nam with. It was a gratifying <br>
experience to chat with old friends that I had'nt heard from<br>
in over 25 years. The web-site is www.switchboard.com<br>
Good luck.Proud to have served with all of you.<br>
MARTIN C. TANGUAY conrad_9@hotmail.com
